# Device packages for the AYN Odin 2 Mini, installed from [pocknix] at the END of
# install_local_packages (after the kernel step, so the metapackage's kernel dep is
# already present). The metapackage pulls pocknix-bsp-odin2mini + pocknix-bsp-common.
# Extra ALARM package names may be listed here too if this device ever needs one.
pocknix-device-odin2mini
